      "id": "PopularPost282562",
      "post_content": "Instead of all these crazy combos of tearing up other people's cards and losing friends, you could just have this with [R&D's Secret Lair](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=R&D's Secret Lair) out on the field. That way, when Chaos Confetti says \"destroy each card in play that a piece touches\", you can quite literally destroy the cards. You don't get the guarantee of your opponent losing all his/her cards, but it's short, simple, and to the point. ",
      "posted_by": "rogelio",
