      "id": "PopularPost345724",
      "post_content": "Here's my [Chaos Orb](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chaos Orb) deck. I have a large stack of [Chaos Confetti](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chaos Confetti) cards at all times because that's my favorite card in the deck. My son built this for me years ago so that I could hang out in card shops without dying of boredom LOL. It's been a long time since I updated it. Obviously a flipping deck, just for fun, but it's still my type of play because I'm not a serious player. I suggest building one for your mom, too!  \n  \nArtifacts  \nx4 [Chaos Orb](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chaos Orb), x4 [Chaos Confetti](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chaos Confetti), x4 [Bottle of Suleiman](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Bottle of Suleiman), x4 [Krark's Thumb](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Krark's Thumb)  \n  \nCreatures  \nx4 [Mijae Djinn](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mijae Djinn), x4 [Wild Wurm](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wild Wurm), x4 [Goblin Bookie](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Goblin Bookie), x2 [Ydwen Efreet](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ydwen Efreet)  \n  \nSorceries, Enchantments, Instants  \nx2 [Fiery Gambit](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fiery Gambit), x2 [Falling Star](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Falling Star), x4 [Game of Chaos](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Game of Chaos), x2 [Mana Clash](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mana Clash), x2 [Chan](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chan)... [(see all)](javascript:void(0);)",
      "posted_by": "Jeremiahs-Mom",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost345724\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">Here's my <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Chaos Orb\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chaos Orb\">Chaos Orb</a> deck.  I have a large stack of <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Chaos Confetti\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chaos Confetti\">Chaos Confetti</a> cards at all times because that's my favorite card in the deck.  My son built this for me years ago so that I could hang out in card shops without dying of boredom LOL.  It's been a long time since I updated it.  Obviously a flipping deck, just for fun, but it's still my type of play because I'm not a serious player.  I suggest building one for your mom, too!<br/><br/>Artifacts<br/>x4 <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Chaos Orb\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chaos Orb\">Chaos Orb</a>, x4 <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Chaos Confetti\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chaos Confetti\">Chaos Confetti</a>, x4 <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Bottle of Suleiman\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Bottle of Suleiman\">Bottle of Suleiman</a>, x4 <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Krark's Thumb\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Krark's Thumb\">Krark's Thumb</a><br/><br/>Creatures<br/>x4 <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mijae Djinn\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mijae Djinn\">Mijae Djinn</a>, x4 <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Wild Wurm\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wild Wurm\">Wild Wurm</a>, x4 <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Goblin Bookie\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Goblin Bookie\">Goblin Bookie</a>, x2 <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Ydwen Efreet\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ydwen Efreet\">Ydwen Efreet</a><br/><br/>Sorceries, Enchantments, Instants<br/>x2 <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Fiery Gambit\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fiery Gambit\">Fiery Gambit</a>, x2 <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Falling Star\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Falling Star\">Falling Star</a>, x4 <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Game of Chaos\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Game of Chaos\">Game of Chaos</a>, x2 <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mana Clash\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mana Clash\">Mana Clash</a>, x2 <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Chan\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chan\">Chan</a>... <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" onclick=\"ExpandPost(event, this, 345724)\">(see all)</a></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '345724'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy102555\">Jeremiahs-Mom</span>\r\n                                (10/12/2013 11:31:35 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/Le